Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H282089&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Keisuke's beloved Ryouko side with GOD?\NAnd who is Kiriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X fights against the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Terrifying Human Genius Plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the twenty-third person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-three elementary and middle school\Nstudents have jumped to their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And not an illness among them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see what GOD would get out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares what their plan is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's making these kids jump?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,While you're wondering what GOD are after,\Nthese incidents keep happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat got your tongue?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You just reminded me of my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows who they'll target next?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump, Ayako!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,With that white silk cloth,\Nyou can fly in the sky all you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,With this silk cloth, I can fly in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful! Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way! Can't you see that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Icarus Death Smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Only death awaits those who stand in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes twenty-four.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Icarus, prepare to receive orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD Chief Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The first stage of your plan to drive children\Nto suicide is already a splendid success.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceed to the second stage at once!\NDrive Dr. Daimonji into an abyss of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wreck his human genius research and\Nrecruit the doctor into GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(0,0)\blur1\bord0\shad0\fscx100\fscy100\1c&HCECFB2&\p1}m 247 268 l 535 268 535 376 247 376
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(392,370)\fs72\1c&H312F2E&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\b1\fscy150}Daimonji
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayako...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cattleyas, your favourite flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:05:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The cattleyas you loved so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, Fuyoko is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister! Sister, why did you have to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! Stupid sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems this Dr. Daimonji has been researching\N'human geniuses' for ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad told me about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently his research can increase a human's intelligence\Ntenfold. He only uses good-hearted children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be terrible if it fell into the wrong hands. This time\Nthe victim was Dr. Daimonji's daughter Ayako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, I'll investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these pictures here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the recipients of my human genius research.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these already intelligent elementary and middle school\Nstudents took this mental stimulant I created.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's who the children in those pictures are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Daimonji, you don't think--?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but worry that these children's\Nmysterious deaths were a side-effect of this medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Ayako, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayako died of unknown causes too.\NOnly one child who's taken my medicine has survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Fuyuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Seyama. An outstanding assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuyoko seems to be falling for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She talks about getting married when she's bigger...\Nbut she's still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't know how much longer Fuyuko has left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, do you mean--?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a good look at that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one to have survived my\Nmedicine thus far is Fuyuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But that also means that Fuyuko is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep crying you'll stick that way.\NCome on, dry your tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Daimonji, that won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I won't let Fuyoko die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord God, by your mercy grant\Nthis faithful soul a peaceful sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,May your holy angels watch\Nover her grave as its keepers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:08:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Free the soul here interred of all its sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her come before the Heavenly Host, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuyoko's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, could Fuyuko have wandered off in her shock?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Find her! Please, find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Fuyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Icarus Death Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're--!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Icarus Death Smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Had enough, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuyuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to keep her out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiriko, you always seem to show up after Ryouko.\NWon't you tell me who you really are?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Ryouko betray me and my dad?\NPlease, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko is my elder sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're twins. But we grew up far away from one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, please console yourself with the fact\Nthat my sister is still your fiancee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fiancee?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that.\NIf it's true, then why did Ryouko--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, I'm your ally.\NI'll leave Fuyoko with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Seyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Seyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Seyama, don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For me... you did this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuyoko, Seyama will be fine now.\NPlease get to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but he got like this fighting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't stay beside him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Seyama has a dream that someday he'll fly in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He never stops talking about it, even while helping dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't think it's a fairytale that humans might fly one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Icarus! Icarus! This is GOD's Chief Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your orders are to kill X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, we have no need for Dr. Daimonji if he won't join GOD.\NKill him at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, Icarus?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your stories are always so wonderful, Seyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,People flying in the sky without planes...\NIt's so romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why angels of all\Ncultures wear white as they fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because white is the colour of a pure heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why they can fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! White has no dirtiness to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I love these white flowers so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Smells nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Icarus...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD Chief Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In accordance with your orders,\NJin Keisuke has been eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. You will next kill Dr. Daimonji and Fuyuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Move aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Seyama, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, what's the rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, doctor!\NThis guy's really Icarus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So you knew, Jin Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to you, Combat Agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Have at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What were they up to? And why did Icarus take off?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Seyama, this is a present from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,An angel flying in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see your face when I gave it to you! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... Fuyuko, will you\Ncome to the lab a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.81,0:17:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly... You will fly in the sky...\NWith the white silk cloth, you can fly free, free...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die... Don't die, Fuyuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful, Fuyuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuyuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiriko, please take care of Fuyuko.\NI'm going to take out Icarus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Icarus is probably after Seyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuyuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Seyama! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Icarus, I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed twenty-three innocent children,\Nincluding Ayako, and you'd even kill Fuyuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see Fuyuko die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother, Icarus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come at me, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Seyama! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of that disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and get rid of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Seyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Icarus, show your real form to Fuyuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to me which form I fight you with!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Revolving Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Seyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Icarus Death Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Seyama was Icarus...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Icarus is beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Seyama said he was happy to meet you...\Nand that he's gone to a far-off place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Keisuke. It's hard for Fuyuko,\Nbut I think she'll grow from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.00,0:22:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've stopped my human genius research for now.\NMaybe human growth is best left to nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I know that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to think I'm going to be the last modified human.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.87,0:22:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider thwarted the evil\NGOD Agency's conspiracies again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.01,0:23:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can protect the world from GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.25,0:23:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ride on, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.58,0:23:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.50,0:23:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD has its sights on a new energy source and orders its monster Atlas to disrupt the research.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The responsibility for the research's security falls to Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But what is the mystery of Ryouko and Kiriko,\Nwho've helped Keisuke in his fight against GOD?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.50,0:23:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Bizarre!? Little Earth, Medium Earth, Big Earth"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.00,0:23:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.00,0:23:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.21,0:23:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.21,0:23:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.20,0:23:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.20,0:23:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.40,0:23:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.40,0:23:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.67,0:24:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.67,0:24:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.84,0:24:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.84,0:24:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.00,0:24:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.00,0:24:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.24,0:24:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.24,0:24:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider